🧠 Key Idea (VERY IMPORTANT)

At MVP stage:

👉 “AI” is NOT ChatGPT
👉 It is rule-based intelligence + data tracking

Example:

User fails “road signs” 3 times
→ System increases probability of those questions

That’s already AI enough for V1

