🧠 AI Logic Implementation (Code-Level Idea)
Weak Topic Query
SELECT topic_id,
       wrong_count::float / (correct_count + wrong_count) AS weakness
FROM topic_performance
WHERE user_id = ?
ORDER BY weakness DESC
LIMIT 3;
Personalized Questions
weak_topics = top 3 topics

questions = 
  70% FROM weak_topics
  30% random

return shuffled(questions)
🔐 Access Control (Critical)

Middleware:

if subscription.expired:
    block access